Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:33.58,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个手 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.29,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把这只人类的手给对方看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:41.18,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后说「请给我一个适合这个手大小的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:47.10,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听清楚了吗 绝不能把另一只手伸出去」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:51.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈说到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:56.64,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「为什么呢？」小狐狸问到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:04.72,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「人类啊 如果知道你是一只狐狸的话不会卖给你手套的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:10.55,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相反 他们还会把你抓起来关到笼子里去」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:17.78,Sakura_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(978.667,646.667)}小樱和秋穗的摇篮曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:19.59,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.26,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,朗读的内容非常清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.60,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.58,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:29.49,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你每天早上早起努力练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.89,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难得利佳借给我图画书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.19,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能好好读出来就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:38.36,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要和雪兔一起去给别人讲故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:43.33,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 雪兔哥在许多地方都在开展朗读志愿者的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.98,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你们俩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:51.46,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还打算再邀请一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.50,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给别人讲故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.05,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋穗你没听说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.60,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.38,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着图画书 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.59,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,It's like a story time（好比是讲故事时间）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.36,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,like reading stories to children（给孩子们讲故事一样）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.50,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.71,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,oh I understand（哦 我懂了）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.31,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是读书啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:16.67,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要读给在儿科的小朋友们听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.50,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.35,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是什么厉害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.42,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.89,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狼也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.33,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大家一起读
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.54,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还可以演绎不同的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.74,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的日语不怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.51,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:40.04,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你在国语课上读的「梦十夜」很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.61,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.35,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小学时候演剧就很糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.04,0:03:48.85,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,演公主的时候很有个性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.64,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,演王子的时候也很赞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.76,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.51,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就 弹钢琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:06.98,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给读书配上合适的伴奏怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.20,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,弹钢琴的大道寺应该更…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.76,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要摄影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.81,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他的脸好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.95,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,遭遇了小樱的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.25,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,李同学的HP立刻就会归零了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 只是伴奏的话我就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:38.87,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.04,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋穗~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.03,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不给你添麻烦的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.59,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.73,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:55.34,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋穗的HP也归零了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:59.29,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狼少爷竟然要做伴奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.03,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知怎么反正就成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.05,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么样的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.27,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是个关于狐狸买手套的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.40,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:11.64,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,它自己不是有皮毛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.66,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,即便有皮毛在严冬时也会冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.73,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事的结局是美好的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.54,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.87,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 如小狼大人所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.42,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在三十分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.09,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用邮件发送给你一个迎合朗读的乐谱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.65,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 您最近情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:48.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狼大人不太经常和我联络
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.41,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,莓林和你已经说了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.10,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.02,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她告诉我在相距很久再一次去日本很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:59.99,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且和朋友们再一次见面非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:07.77,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她还告诉我 你看起来好像做出了什么沉重的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:14.32,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你从日本回家 又从家启程去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:20.24,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚这是你妈妈给予你的一场残酷试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:24.74,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 你真的变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.61,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还是很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.20,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对于我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.66,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的使命就是小狼少爷无论遇到任何情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:35.73,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都要尽力帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.70,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:44.59,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请打开视频让我看看你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.06,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐她们的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.06,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.38,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:56.95,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再给我发送一些食物照片以及占存储空间的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:01.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看见好吃的食物以及可爱的我们不应该令你开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.39,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.79,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.18,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,温伯 乐谱的事情就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.26,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.70,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 那我们就发一些更长的视频给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:18.98,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:31.44,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为你太温柔 所以我才会担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.82,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸钻到妈妈的肚子下面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.65,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,边走边用那闪闪发光的圆眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.33,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不停的环顾周围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.49,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不久 它们的前途…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.21,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是「前方」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:56.03,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.32,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:04.25,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把需要注意的地方 以及犯错的地方都写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不在书上做笔记吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.34,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在书上随便写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:16.92,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是作者呕心沥血做出的书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.62,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋穗小姐真的很喜欢书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:22.63,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.18,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,练了这么久 喉咙也干了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:35.14,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用特地纠正的呢 秋穗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.49,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不…不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.25,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是蜂蜜红茶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.73,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对 蜂蜜对喉咙好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.84,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请一起吃点巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:47.78,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:54.34,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有两个人吃的话 有一点多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:57.62,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 一定能解决掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.27,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都会装到我的纤纤素体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.94,Sakura_picture2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HE89C5D&\bord0\fs90\pos(986.666,374.667)}朗读会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.94,Sakura_picture1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1285.333,864.667)}{\c&H999E9B&\bord0}银河铁道之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.94,Sakura_picture1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1264,976.667)}{\c&H999E9B&\bord0}去买手套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:13.72,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乔邦妮内心百感交集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.91,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话也没说就从博士面前离去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.63,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要尽快把牛奶带给母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.70,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让母亲知道父亲要回来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:29.65,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,便不遗余力的沿河向小镇跑去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.40,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.58,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.29,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.73,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,天花板在哪里呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:39.86,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.39,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:42.46,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.91,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雪兔哥好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.31,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是…我没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.22,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:52.67,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.17,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你们两个都努力练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.54,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.87,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请换上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.31,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,寒冬从北方而至
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:28.74,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来到了狐狸居住的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:35.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}某天早上 小狐狸正要从洞穴里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.00,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是准备了衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.22,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些简单的服饰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.02,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那小子拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.52,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让他能感到舒心才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:49.08,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我就先放过他了 也就这次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:55.30,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱小孩的手冻伤的话就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.26,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是狐狸妈妈打算在夜晚去小镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:04.11,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,买双适合小男孩手的毛线手套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:09.20,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑的夜晚展开了巨大的黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.57,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,将原野和森林吞噬其中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过雪太过洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:19.44,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样包裹 仍散发白光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:26.23,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不一会儿 前方出现零星光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.68,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,随后小狐狸看到后问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:36.78,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 原来星星会落到那么低的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.34,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:46.16,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说着狐狸妈妈腿就软了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:49.64,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是镇上的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.61,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那镇上的灯火时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:12:00.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈就会想起以前和朋友去镇子时的可怕遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.77,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不听劝告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:09.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸朋友打算去偷某户人家的鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:13.73,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被住户发现 穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.75,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易才逃命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:24.37,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 狐狸妈妈只好让小狐狸自己去小镇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.38,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 伸出你的小手手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.81,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.20,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后握住小狐狸的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:41.16,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿那只手就变成了可爱人类孩子的手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.50,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:45.45,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.08,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人类的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.33,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:56.37,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到镇上后 会有很多人类的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:02.21,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要找到圆帽子招牌挂着的房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:07.66,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到后 你就咚咚去敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.23,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后说晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:16.09,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样之后 里面的人会稍稍的打开门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:23.71,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就把这个人类的手伸过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:29.20,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说请给我合适这只手的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:34.35,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗 千万不能把这只手伸过去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.40,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈嘱咐道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,自行车的招牌 眼镜的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.45,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他各种招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.87,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有些是用新的油漆涂色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:53.69,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有些像是古老的墙壁褪色了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:14:02.01,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过才到小镇的小狐狸并不知道那些到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.76,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最后小狐狸终于找到了帽子店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.89,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈反复嘱咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.70,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大黑色礼帽的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.62,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在蓝色灯光的照射下挂在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:24.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸按妈妈说的敲了门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:25.99,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:32.09,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,随后店内传来一阵轻微声响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.20,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,门开了一寸左右的缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:40.95,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,灯光长长的投射在了路上的白雪上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:45.37,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸被光线照晕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.16,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慌乱中小狐狸不小心伸错了手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:57.01,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把那只妈妈反复强调不能伸出去的手伸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.57,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.17,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不能那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.54,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会像其他狐狸那样被追赶的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.33,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.45,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.83,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.02,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我一双适合这只手的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:37.60,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,随后帽子店的老板被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.78,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是狐狸的手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:43.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一只狐狸的手在向我要手套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:49.81,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是想用树叶来买我的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.40,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请先付钱 老板说道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:16:00.60,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸老实的将自己攥着的两枚铜钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.90,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,交给了帽子店老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:10.24,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子店的老板把钱放到食指上碰了碰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,发出了叮叮的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.75,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是树叶 是真正的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:23.39,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,于是老板从架子上取下儿童毛线手套
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:26.35,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放到了小狐狸的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.89,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸说了谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.82,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就踏上了回家的路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:37.98,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「虽然妈妈说过人类是可怕的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,其实没那么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.97,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了我的手也没有做什么」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸这样想着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.41,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,当它路过一个窗子下面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.76,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,传出了人类的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.16,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.48,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多么动听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:01.57,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多么沉稳的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.56,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.02,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:16.01,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在妈妈的轻抚下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.29,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:22.01,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:27.43,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在妈妈的轻抚下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.27,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:36.44,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是人类的妈妈的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:40.30,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 小狐狸睡觉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:46.54,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈也会用这样温柔的声音哄它入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.70,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,听了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:52.74,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸突然开始想妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.98,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,奔向狐狸妈妈那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:08.06,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈正焦急颤抖地等待着小狐狸的归来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:12.48,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子回来后 便将它拥入温暖的怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.76,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福得仿佛要哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:19.58,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,两只狐狸回到了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.77,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮升起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.92,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸的皮毛闪耀着金色的光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:29.12,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,足迹里存着蔚蓝的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.88,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人类一点也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.50,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:39.00,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我弄错了把真正的手伸出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:42.96,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是帽子店老板没有抓我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:47.53,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我了这么暖和的手套
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:53.32,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说着把戴着手套的两只手给妈妈看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.87,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈惊呼了一声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.63,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:05.51,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.23,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸妈妈如此默念着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.83,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子店老板真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.13,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:21.53,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,弹一首电视里的曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.42,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐唱歌好好听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.39,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.63,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.81,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么时候再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.98,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.85,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:35.86,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.24,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:44.42,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.46,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然中途发生了不少事情 但我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:50.34,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过下次想坐在观众席上看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.52,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天知世已经录下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:55.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:55.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,release
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.86,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:57.86,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,Record
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:05.46,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在开始之前我就用了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.88,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.05,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把记录的东西显现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.50,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是知世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.71,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我也录进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.51,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个大叔是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.46,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.59,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.94,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:50.53,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的没有录到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.10,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:02.42,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:04.95,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,月发邮件来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:08.11,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多今天到保质期的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.58,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.61,0:21:11.71,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:13.14,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.87,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.90,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,保质期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:22.29,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得小可的话即使过期一周都没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.21,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:27.97,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.12,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱使用记录的卡牌看到的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.96,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是30多年以前使用的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:41.72,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和今天的朗读会上护士穿的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.22,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:48.01,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用卡牌拍摄下了过去的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.01,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:58.82,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱好像不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:04.62,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过的有能力拍摄过去的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.92,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,除了库洛以外只有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:14.19,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有库洛的血缘 继承了那个卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:17.51,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,并且把它变成了自己的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:19.71,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:23.49,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道她魔力变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.38,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没想到已经到了这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:30.11,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱的魔力在变强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.52,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,强到超出想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.62,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,联络艾力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.12,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何也要…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:12.18,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.27,0:24:15.42,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也元气满满的交给小可吧栏目
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.44,0:24:16.45,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这次介绍的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:18.43,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋穗的玩偶 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:20.25,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的身体 和水蓝色的围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.28,0:24:23.15,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,左耳装饰着鲜明的耳饰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.16,0:24:24.41,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,右耳的上端弯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:25.93,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,特征是右眼的泪痣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.35,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为只是个有成熟感的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.37,0:24:31.36,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到令人震惊的是她居然是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:31.07,Sakura_picture2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz11.57\pos(1448,916)}闭眼                     睁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:33.02,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉演员都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.04,0:24:34.64,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待之后会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.65,0:24:36.45,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太期待了都有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.46,0:24:38.07,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想吃手工制作巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.08,0:24:39.54,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下集见
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,/下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.13,0:24:45.41,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和小狼两个人拜访了曾祖父的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.87,0:24:47.72,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要给我们的东西是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:49.11,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请看下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.37,0:24:51.08,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱和彩虹和爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.56,0:24:54.35,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和小樱一起 封印解除
Comment: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.61,Sakura_text,NTP,0,0,0,,--staff--
